'''Symbian''' was an obscure language that died out in approximately [[30,000 BBY]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], it was used as part of an elaborate code for correspondence between [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] spies.

